Quickstrike:




"That's the area Rowdy Wolf is." Quickstrike said to Dark Mouse. "He's uh 
Predacon. Ah met 'im there when ah got fed up wit' Hell Beast's troops. Ah 
was thinkin' we can send one of our fliers out there and get 'im out here t' 
help." He turned his shoulder and looked over it the best he could. A lot of 
times the plate behind his head restricted the visione behind him. He glared 
at Terrorsaur up the large stalactmite. "Ya think ya can give those 
cooridinates to Terrorsaur?"
